# Raspberry Pi 4 BSP Project (Custom LED Driver)

## Build Instructions

### 1. Local Configuration (`build/conf/local.conf`)
Add the following lines to the end of your `conf/local.conf` file to enable the custom driver and device tree overlay.

```bitbake
# 1. Install Driver & Kernel Modules
IMAGE_INSTALL:append = " kernel-modules simple-driver"

# 2. Add Device Tree Overlay to config.txt automatically
RPI_EXTRA_CONFIG = " \n \
    dtoverlay=my-led \n \
"

# 3. Copy .dtbo file to Boot Partition (Crucial!)
IMAGE_BOOT_FILES:append = " my-led.dtbo;overlays/my-led.dtbo"